| Token | Value |
|---|---|
| Primary Color | `#1E3A5F` (Biru Tua) |
| Accent | `#F59E0B` (Amber/Gold) |
| Background | `#F8FAFC` |
| Font | `Plus Jakarta Sans` (Google Fonts) |
| Border Radius | `16px` (card), `12px` (button) |
| Shadow | `0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)` |

