## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Teknologi |
|---|---|
| Framework | **Next.js 14** (App Router) |
| Styling | **Tailwind CSS** |
| Icons | **Lucide React** |
| Date Picker | **react-day-picker** |
| Animasi | **Framer Motion** |
| Gambar | `next/image` (optimized) |
| Data | JSON lokal / Supabase (opsional) |

