## 📦 Struktur Folder

```
/app
  /villa
    page.tsx              ← Daftar Villa
    /[slug]/page.tsx      ← Detail Villa
  /hotel-cabin
    page.tsx              ← Daftar Cabin
    /[slug]/page.tsx      ← Detail Cabin
  /jeep
    page.tsx              ← Daftar Paket Jeep
    /[slug]/page.tsx      ← Detail Paket Jeep
  /wisata
    page.tsx              ← Daftar Tempat Wisata
    /[slug]/page.tsx      ← Detail Wisata
  /booking/[slug]/page.tsx
/components
  Navbar.tsx
  VillaCard.tsx
  JeepCard.tsx           ← Card khusus jeep
  SearchBar.tsx
  SearchBarJeep.tsx      ← Search destinasi + tanggal
  BentoGrid.tsx
  FacilityBadge.tsx
  PromoBanner.tsx
  WisataCard.tsx         ← Card 4-col wisata
  SearchBarWisata.tsx    ← Search di dalam hero
  FilterTabs.tsx         ← Explore | Atraksi | Aktivitas
  VideoSlider.tsx        ← Slider video reels wisata
  TourTimeline.tsx       ← Stepper rundown tour
/data
  villas.json
  cabins.json
  jeeps.json
  wisata.json            ← Data tempat wisata
/public/images/
```

